    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of raw power and pixelated chaos in this <strong>arcade-inspired beat ‘em up adventure</strong>!<br>Play as a group of brutal, muscle-bound mutant friends who aren’t afraid to smash, punch, and slam their way through hordes of enemies. With every stage, the stakes rise and the action gets wilder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/d03c5be2756636e740bc98273a6ebed2.poster.avif?t=1771368194\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/d03c5be2756636e740bc98273a6ebed2.webm?t=1771368194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/d03c5be2756636e740bc98273a6ebed2.mp4?t=1771368194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way across <strong>12 challenging stages</strong>, each packed with enemies, bosses, and explosive action. Alongside the classic side-scrolling beat ‘em up gameplay, you’ll encounter <strong>unique stage mechanics</strong> that keep every level fresh and unpredictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the golden age of arcade games and brought to life in <strong>stylish pixel art</strong>, this game delivers pure retro energy with a modern punch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/3776812ebafbaf0a6e9968218742d39c.poster.avif?t=1771368194\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/3776812ebafbaf0a6e9968218742d39c.webm?t=1771368194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060240/extras/3776812ebafbaf0a6e9968218742d39c.mp4?t=1771368194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic <strong>beat ‘em up action</strong> with a modern twist.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 stages</strong> full of enemies, bosses, and surprises.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique stage mechanics that go beyond standard fighting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cast of <strong>badass mutant heroes</strong> with over-the-top style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nostalgic pixel art visuals with arcade vibes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your friends (mutant or not) and get ready to <strong>kick, punch, and smash your way to victory</strong>!</p>",
